<h2>Electroreductive Polymerisation and Corrosion Resistance of <i>trans</i>-[RuCl<sub>2</sub>(vpy)<sub>4</sub>] on
Nd-Fe-B Magnets in Na<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>  Solution.</h2>
</dir>


  Bandeira, M.C.E.<sup>1</sup>; Prochnow, F. D.<sup> 1</sup>; Costa, I.<sup> 2</sup>; Franco, C.V.<sup> 1
